<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Discussion Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1, p {
            margin: 0 0 20px 0;
        }
        .banner {
            height: 50px;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #8254F8;
            text-align: right;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 40px;
            gap: 5px;
            padding: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #8254F8;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="banner">
            <img src='https://discoursefy-public-bucket.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/Logo.jpg' /> <span> Discoursefy.</span>
        </section>
        <div class="wrapper">
        <h1>Reminder: Upcoming Discussion in 5 Minutes</h1>
        <p>
            Dear {{ userName }},
        </p>
        <p>
            This is a friendly reminder that the upcoming discussion, "{{ discussionTitle }}," is scheduled to begin in just 5 minutes.
        </p>
        <p>
            📅 <strong>Discussion will start with in {{ remainingTime }} minutes </strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="{{ discussionUrl }}" class="btn">🔗 Join Discussion</a>
        </p>
        <p>
            Join us for an engaging session where we'll discuss {{ discussionDescription }} and exchange ideas.
        </p>
        <p>
            Looking forward to your participation!
        </p>
        <p>
            Best regards,<br>
            Discoursefy
        </p>
    </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
